I&#39;m on mobile so I apologize for formatting. You can just provide a class based on a prop. 

    &lt;body class=&quot;[isInView ? &#39;view-class&#39; : &#39;&#39;]&quot;&gt;
     &lt;Linker @click=&quot;goToView&quot; /&gt;
